{"id":428669,"date":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":24}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"154","ytitle":"","mtitle":"王献之写字","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1962\\03\\623o041501.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(十四)有一次，献之假冒父亲之名，写了一幅字，贴在壁上。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1962\\03\\623o041502.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(十五)他父亲看了，以为是自己写的，但想了半天，总记不起这幅字是什么时候写的。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1962\\03\\623o041503.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(十六)父亲知道是献之的手笔，心中大为高兴。后来献之的书法终于成名，人称其父子为“二王”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(完)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海人民美术出版社供稿</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>杨根相,丁中一</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>杨根相　改编丁中一　绘</FONT>"}]}